Uploading patch which provides method to return all the properties of configuration object as a string of Json format.

The Json format is as follows:

{ "Properties" : [
       { "Key" : <key>,
          "Value" : <value>,
          "isFinal" : <true if the property is set to final>
          "resource" : <resource name which loads this property most recently> }
   ] }
